# Scene.AnchorCollection.Element

**Type Alias**

The type of element traversed by the iterator.

## Declaration

```swift
typealias Element = HasAnchoring
```

## Iterating over the collection

- **makeIterator()**: Returns an iterator over the elements of the collection.
- **Scene.AnchorCollection.Iterator**: An iterator that presents the elements of the collection.
